{"tid":1701126,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"警察本質係先保護政權，後保護市民","createTime":"2019-11-09T01:14:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T04:42:17.000Z","uid":149978,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c2460855d99b7de0b58356022d78b7f1659448fc","tid":1701126,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T01:14:57.000Z","msg":"邊個出糧就服務邊個<br />\n<br />\n警察受政府出糧，所以係服務政府<br />\n<br />\n政府由市民出糧，理應服務市民。<br />\n但歷史係所有政權都係靠戰爭和暴力出黎，<br />\n所以政府有警察就唔駛怕市民。<br />\n<br />\n警察如果企在市民一方，唔企政權一方會點？<br />\n政權除左警察，仲有軍隊。<br />\n咁咪出動解放軍鎮壓你們囉。<br />\n<br />\n如果香港解放軍都企在市民上又點，<br />\n老共就會派軍隊向香港宣戰。<br />\n<br />\n除非全國解放軍和警察都想推翻中共，<br />\n否則香港人只能享受被老共強暴的樂趣。"},{"pid":"3ca3b3f93d5b0b115434493aea650ecb0894dcdd","tid":1701126,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T01:16:56.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">入去rt + like + reply</span><br />\nSenator Rubio都知道周同學死訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1192876824868671488?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1192876824868671488%3Fs%3D21&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOJsm%2Bn8Fwo%2F6aJUx9arcu0Q%3D&h=e4a31424\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1192876824868671488%3Fs%3D21&h=c4dc6427\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1192876824868671488?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n（最新）Senator Scott 都出聲講議員被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1192902065783296006?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1192902065783296006%3Fs%3D19&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOJsm%2Bn8Fwo%2F6aJUx9arcu0Q%3D&h=84fd91b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1192902065783296